title: Ben Folds - Canberra 2011 (MP3).mp3
description:
Ben Folds at the Royal Theatre, Canberra, Australia (Wed, May 11, 2011)

Recorded using a Blue Mikey on iPhone 3G. Not too bad for what it is. If you were there it's a nice recording to have. If not, it's still pretty good. :)

Ben's tour to promote the Lonely Avenue album. The tour was supported by Kate Miller-Heidke who appears on several songs during Ben's performance.
